[{"rendered_body":"\u003cp\u003eruby 2.6からはRubyで添え字付きでループを回し、かつ0以外の数値で開始したいとき\u003ccode\u003ezip(1..)\u003c/code\u003e出来るのでチル📻\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"code-frame\" data-lang=\"rb\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"highlight\"\u003e\u003cpre\u003e\u003cspan class=\"n\"\u003efruits\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e[\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e'apple'\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e'orange'\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e'melon'\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e]\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"n\"\u003efruits\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nf\"\u003ezip\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"mi\"\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e..\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e)\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e|\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"n\"\u003efruit\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"n\"\u003ei\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e|\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003eputs\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"s2\"\u003e\"\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"si\"\u003e#{\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"n\"\u003ei\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"si\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s2\"\u003e: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"si\"\u003e#{\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"n\"\u003efruit\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"si\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s2\"\u003e\"\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"c1\"\u003e# 1: apple\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"c1\"\u003e# 2: orange\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"c1\"\u003e# 3: melon\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/pre\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://qiita.com/jnchito/items/2b909a3d75728f99bbbe\" id=\"reference-08e1aeea02cdb4d1f58b\"\u003eeach_with_indexには引数を渡せない、わけではない\u003c/a\u003eを読んで韻を踏みたくなったので書きました。\u003c/p\u003e\n","body":"ruby 2.6からはRubyで添え字付きでループを回し、かつ0以外の数値で開始したいとき`zip(1..)`出来るのでチル📻\n\n```rb\nfruits = ['apple', 'orange', 'melon']\nfruits.zip(1..) {|fruit, i| puts \"#{i}: #{fruit}\" }\n# 1: apple\n# 2: orange\n# 3: melon\n```\n\n[each_with_indexには引数を渡せない、わけではない](https://qiita.com/jnchito/items/2b909a3d75728f99bbbe)を読んで韻を踏みたくなったので書きました。\n","coediting":false,"comments_count":5,"created_at":"2018-08-09T12:39:33+09:00","group":null,"id":"c313ff6573e1bbca3446","likes_count":3,"private":false,"reactions_count":0,"tags":[{"name":"Ruby","versions":[]}],"title":"rubyは1..でzip出来るのでチル","updated_at":"2018-08-09T12:54:08+09:00","url":"https://qiita.com/hanachin_/items/c313ff6573e1bbca3446","user":{"description":"既婚バイ","facebook_id":"seiei.higa","followees_count":166,"followers_count":120,"github_login_name":"hanachin","id":"hanachin_","items_count":55,"linkedin_id":"","location":"Naha, Okinawa, Japan","name":"Seiei Miyagi","organization":"YassLab","permanent_id":2074,"profile_image_url":"https://qiita-image-store.s3.amazonaws.com/0/2074/profile-images/1511092027","twitter_screen_name":"hanachin_","website_url":""},"page_views_count":null}]